


Audio module
Local storage (…/files/audio/; later trasnfered in batch to CloudStorage and/or Firestore; eg., at midnight): 
1. audio file (dedup'd and suppressed) named with 'audio + date/timestsamp in format of yyyymmddhhmmSSsss'
2. audio.signal.rmsDb calculated from audio.dedupe.suppressed + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss + url to audio file in cloud storage

Cache (in memory; 30-min window): 
1. audio.signal.rmsDb + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss

