Motion module 
Local storage (…/files/motion/; later trasnfered in batch to Firestore; eg., at midnight):
1. motion.imu.accel.{x,y,z}Ms2 + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss
2. motion.imu.gyro.{x,y,z}RadS + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss
3. motion.step.sessionTotal + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss

Cache (in memory; 30-min window): 
1. motion.step.sessionTotal + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss


