GPS module 

Local storage (…/files/gps/; later trasnfered in batch to Firestore; eg., at midnight):
1. [gps.fix.latitudeDegrees, gps.fix.longitudeDegrees, gps.weather.sunScore0To10, date/timestsamp in format of yyyymmddhhmmSSsss + metadata] -- either array or json format.

Cache (in memory; 30-min window): 
1. gps.weather.sunScore0To10 + metadata + yyyymmddhhmmSSsss

